- 1/3628800 ≈ 0.000000276
- -1/39916800 ≈ -0.0000000251
- 1/479001600 ≈ 0.00000000209

Sum ≈ 0.367879

Now 12! = 479001600

So D₁₂ = 479001600 × 0.367879 ≈ 176214841

The total number of possible outcomes when 12 students each roll a 12-sided die is 12^12.

